  "detailed_description": "The world has come to an end. Welcome to the unique Dieselpunk 2D Action Adventure game.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Become a hero whose consciousness has been transferred to a mechanical shell.<br></li><li> Explore a detailed 2D world. Unique architecture and traditional frame-by-frame animation awaits you.<br></li><li> Ammo and resources are limited, use them wisely.<br></li><li> Find out the truth behind the death of an entire Archipelago.<br></li><li> Engage in an unequal battle with the rebellious mechatrons army.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/0d4621823074c41ba23120d5a3a6d297.poster.avif?t=1711642494\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/0d4621823074c41ba23120d5a3a6d297.webm?t=1711642494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/0d4621823074c41ba23120d5a3a6d297.mp4?t=1711642494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/0db9ecd73319a800741165374544dac9.poster.avif?t=1711642494\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/0db9ecd73319a800741165374544dac9.webm?t=1711642494\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/0db9ecd73319a800741165374544dac9.mp4?t=1711642494\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1224030/extras/097984990c7373287